## Scoring and game rules

- Define and document the complete fantasy rules:
  - Points awarded from match, set and result data
  - Captain multiplier and whether bench players score
  - Treatment of incomplete squads at the deadline
  - Free transfers per window and any penalties for extra transfers
- Calculate `player_match_stats` from imported Stupa results.
- Write player round points to `fantasy_team_gameweek_players` snapshots.
- Calculate and store each team's total in `fantasy_team_gameweek_points`.
- Update global leaderboards to use stored gameweek totals instead of the live squad.
- Make the scoring pipeline idempotent so corrected results can be safely recalculated.

## Automation and operations

- Schedule the existing Stupa schedule and result importers with GitHub Actions.
- Run round scoring automatically after completed results are imported.
- Add monitoring for failed Cron runs or locked gameweeks without squad snapshots.
- Add an admin workflow for reconciling unmatched Stupa players before scoring.

## Product features

- Add player statistics pages with match and fantasy-point history.
- Show each team's snapshotted squad and player points for previous rounds.
- Build private league creation, invite, membership and leaderboard UI.
- Add transfer tracking and display remaining free transfers once the rules are decided.

## Testing

- Create small development-only SQL test scripts for setting gameweek deadlines,
  simulating open/closed transfer windows, triggering snapshots, and restoring
  the original timestamps after manual testing.
- Test the full lock cycle: window closes, changes are rejected, snapshots are
  created once, and changes reopen at `unlock_at`.
- Add automated tests for:
  - Four starters, two bench players, captain and budget validation
  - Player selection, replacement and main/bench swaps
  - Transfer-window enforcement in server actions and RLS
  - Snapshot idempotency and one player row per team/gameweek
  - Incomplete squads at the deadline
  - Captain multipliers and gameweek point totals
- Run an end-to-end import and scoring test against another completed league:
  https://sbtfeventsott.stupaevents.com/events/182/315/2/5/5
